{"tid":783111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"福布斯：24歲賭徒舒淇中國首創blockchain社交網","createTime":"2018-08-17T09:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T15:27:39.000Z","uid":165773,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"195ef885474c56cea6794364b80a3afa308c2db9","tid":783111,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:50:46.000Z","msg":"北京舒淇小姐（音譯）數學幾好<br />\n2013年去美國加州做交流生果陣<br />\n中意左同人玩poker 當時未夠21歲<br />\n但係加州法例特別容許倒<br />\n仲讚舒淇玩得好勁<br />\n<br />\nanyway佢online 同offline都玩<br />\n識左好多人 有人玩果陣吹水<br />\n講起bitcoin 舒琪覺得好正<br />\n佢開始堀bitcoin 同埋佢將<br />\n所有poker贏既錢都<br />\n買哂做bitcoin <br />\n<br />\n番到北京都繼續堀 同買bitcoin<br />\n2014年佢最多擁有50000粒<br />\n當時賣左兩萬粒cash in480萬美元<br />\n佢而家應該 最少仲有3萬粒...<br />\n<br />\n就係咁佢2016年用少少錢開公司<br />\n整好多blockchain game仔<br />\n其中一個「加密狗」幾多人玩<br />\n但同一年facebook比人話<br />\n有濫用私隱問題<br />\n刺激倒舒淇一個idea<br />\n決定開發叫ono既blockchain社交app<br />\nono無管理員/團隊既戈<br />\n完全地decentralized<br />\nblocks 唔可以用CPU9堀<br />\n而係要求user貼高質內容<br />\n換like換番來<br />\n<br />\n今年4月出左beta版<br />\n而家8月已經有3百萬user<br />\n內容以英文為主<br />\nono資金係中韓合資<br />\n暫時有1600萬美金<br />\n76個員工 15個係分佈界各地<br />\n<br />\n舒淇解釋佢個app<br />\n「ono係完全民主地運作，user貼既任何資料都真正屬於user，多人like個系統就會發currency作獎勵。<br />\n英國科學家Berners發明internet果陣<br />\n係想比人自由交換資訊/知識<br />\ninternet應該屬於全人類<br />\n但係sosad而家internet出現好多<br />\ncentralized平台s<br />\n全球十大科技公司收入係<br />\n主力賣用戶資料/私隱比<br />\n廣告客etc賺錢！」<br />\n<br />\n舒淇話ono既blockchain系統<br />\n係完全地decentralized<br />\n令用戶擁有番自己data<br />\n所以佢地讀唔倒賣唔倒user data<br />\n舒淇話ono係一個<br />\ndapp而唔係普通app<br />\ndecentralized app 咁解<br />\n<br />\n佢既目標係超越Facebook成為最受歡迎社交平台：「我中意贏多過賺錢！」聽落有D爛賭。<br />\nono 於Google playstore已上架<br />\niOS今個月尾都會有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/bensin/2018/08/16/chinas-first-blockchain-social-network-is-the-brainchild-of-a-24-year-old-female-poker-player/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fbensin%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2Fchinas-first-blockchain-social-network-is-the-brainchild-of-a-24-year-old-female-poker-player%2F&d=bO0u9ZGjfLMWtTGwNArufMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=817774a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.forbes.com/sites/bensin/2018/08/16/chinas-first-blockchain-social-network-is-the-brainchild-of-a-24-year-old-female-poker-player/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/174146_78bb65ad4e0d1fb4a43fb1563e93d153.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F174146_78bb65ad4e0d1fb4a43fb1563e93d153.png&h=73336583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個app：）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 將引發多省獨立 支解中共<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲早比習種一野ban死"},{"pid":"54de3841fee006aa3f1f80de4806fbde17d78797","tid":783111,"uid":65128,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:56:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8df9666d5d902ababa20c7e3f3dd5b488b21dc22","tid":783111,"uid":90890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54de3841fee006aa3f1f80de4806fbde17d78797","tid":783111,"uid":65128,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:56:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"真頭正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46aeae5f36aa217212bc5f467844e2e7b0c5f925","tid":783111,"uid":34186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:59:21.000Z","msg":"冇邀請碼都玩唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ce851ffab55228bc8997692a5b1f99779b4740","tid":783111,"uid":41204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:01:46.000Z","msg":"blockchain同linkedlist有咩分別"},{"pid":"1183df3aa5838a258b41d3e716f5b762